title: CFB BOWL RISERS AND FALLERS
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, Dusty Dvoracek, and Todd McShay examine the 2022 NFL Draft's top prospect performances from the 2022 Bowl Season. Which player saw their stock rise and which saw their draft stock fall? Find out on the CFB Live Podcast.
